      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the helplines. i just... i feel like i'm just existing. like i'm just a ghost in this house. every time i look at his empty bed i just feel this huge wave of exhaustion. like, what is even the point of trying to \"get better\" when everything that made life worth it is just gone? it feels like i'm just waiting for something to end.",
